findings.title: Rounding error
findings.description: In Solidity, division before multiplication can cause rounding errors.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges to perform various actions including adding/removing unlocked addresses, bots, and pairs, triggering _allowTransfer, changing bot's and user's block seconds, minimum number of tokens before swap, liquidity and burning fee, marketing and global reward divisor, enabling swap and liquify, withdrawing contract BNBs, changing marketing and global reward addresses, and buyBackUpperLimit.
